This is my first mod which is just a slight enhancement of the Proudspire Manor Enhanced mod made by Lenox47. If there are any bugs please notify me immediately so i can get straight on that. This is V1.0 of the mod but if anyone asks or comments saying. \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Its nice can you make a V2.0?\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" I can immediately get on that aswell. Iam planning on doing further enhancements some of which i have already done and will be uploading shortly. If anyone has any suggestions i am all ears.Thank you. And please take the time to visit the original mod author and endorse huis mod.
